# Antigravity Rules

## Shell Execution (Windows)
- ENV: Windows. Always use 'cmd /c' for all shell executions instead of standard calls.
- Force shell executions to terminate.

## Package Management
- Always check the workspace root for the presence of `pnpm-lock.yaml` or `package-lock.json` before executing commands to determine whether the project uses `pnpm` or `npm`.
- Run commands using the detected package manager accordingly.

